348
00:38:13,169 --> 00:38:15,630
You make a brown line
and kinda smudge it in.

349
00:38:15,755 --> 00:38:19,426
It has to be real subtle
so as no one'll notice it.

350
00:38:19,551 --> 00:38:22,637
But... What are you smiling about?

351
00:38:22,762 --> 00:38:25,807
I'm impressed that
you know so much about this.

352
00:38:25,932 --> 00:38:28,435
- You're not interested at all.
- Yes, I am.

353
00:38:28,560 --> 00:38:32,147
