386
00:40:42,027 --> 00:40:44,863
It was a great wire.
He could be blocks away

387
00:40:44,988 --> 00:40:48,033
and you could hear everything
within 1 0 feet of him.

388
00:40:48,158 --> 00:40:51,119
- Hey, Milt! How ya doin'?
- Hello, Freddie.

389
00:40:51,244 --> 00:40:53,955
- Good to see ya.
- You look good.

390
00:40:54,080 --> 00:40:57,250
- You too. You look great in that get-up.
- Thanks.

391
00:40:57,834 --> 00:41:01,171
So, uh... I brought
somebody here I want you to meet.

392
00:41:01,296 --> 00:41:03,340
Captain Kennedy, this is Milt.

393
00:41:03,465 --> 00:41:05,634
Who the fuck wants to meet him?

