405
00:41:52,305 --> 00:41:53,682
$1,000?!

406
00:41:53,807 --> 00:41:57,978
I'm gettin' this clear as a bell
on tape and I start to hear the static.

407
00:41:58,103 --> 00:42:02,691
You think you can ... ?
